                     <interp inst="t17710911-78-off421" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17710911-78-off421" type="offenceSubcategory" value="animalTheft"></interp>
               stealing a black mare, value 5 l.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17710911-78-victim872" type="victimName">
                     Thomas
                      Lowden
                  <interp inst="t17710911-78-victim872" type="surname" value="Lowden"></interp>
